# KBM Frontend Coder

## Stack

- WPF .NET 8 — **solo Windows**
- Palette da `docs/ux/style-guide.md` (primary #3B82F6, topbar #1E293B, sidebar #0F172A)
- Layout shell: TopBar 48px + SideNav 220px + StatusBar 28px (`docs/ux/guidelines.md`)
- Font Segoe UI 14px, righe griglia 32px
- RDP-optimized: no animazioni fluide, bottoni min 32×32px

## Wireframes

Riferimento: `docs/ux/wireframes/` — implementare in WPF, non web.

